node.text: This is the brand new Ferrari 812 Competizione and a very first look to check it out! Join me at Fiorano, Ferrari's test track in Maranello, Italy, to walk around the new limited edition super-GT and go through all of the details. #Ferrari #812Competizione #812 #Shmee150

node.title: Check Out the New FERRARI 812 COMPETIZIONE! First Look

node.text: The gullwing doors on the SLS AMG (and in this case the epic Black Series) aren't just for show, they also do a pretty good job of access when space is tight. Here's a perfect example next to my Supra of how little space you need, which you might well find surprising! #Mercedes #SLSAMG #BlackSeries #Gullwing #Shmee150

node.title: SLS AMG Gullwing Doors are Winning!

node.text: The GT8 Club head to the Aston Martin factory for a meet up and that means we can also check out the spec room for the new Valkyrie hypercar!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tim - Shmee on July 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: Welcome to @theshmeemobiles, my @mercedesamg GT Black Series! The journey is only just beginning with collection from @mercedesbenz_retailgroup in Graphite Grey Magno, a true Batmobile if ever there was one, but believe me when I say there's a lot to come. From how much I enjoy my SLS Black Series, and the various AMG GT Rs that I've owned, I cannot wait to get this car out and about. As I've said, it is going to change to AMG Solarbeam yellow, it's going to be going ASAP to the @nuerburgring and a visit to @opus_innovation but first, back to @theshmuseum! #Mercedes #AMG #GTBlackSeries #Shmeemobile #collectionday #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 18, 2021 tagging @mercedesamg, @mercedesbenz_retailgroup, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.

node.text: It's a @mercedesamg kind of day! The new addition to @theshmeemobiles has arrived at long last and today is the day to reveal it, then bring it to @theshmuseum to join the collection! My love for the GT platform is no secret, having owned a number of them in recent years, but this is the ultimate incarnation and the one I've been longing to start putting miles on throughout some delays this year. Let's go! #Mercedes #AMG #GTBlackSeries #Shmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 16, 2021 tagging @ferrari, @hrowenferrari, @shmee150wastaken, and @ferrariuk. May be an image of car and text that says 'ferrari.com'.

node.text: Checking out the new @ferrari 296 GTB! They've managed to give it 830hp from the new 3l TT V6 with an electric motor, all to the rear wheels, while adding the latest tech from the curved screen to touch control steering wheel. Visually there are clues from numerous other Ferrari models, and this car also wears the Assetto Fiorano with a track focused set of shock absorbers, more carbon fibre, lexan rear glass and more, plus the optional painted livery. Like the older Dino models, the name comes from the 2.992cc V6 and Gran Turismo Berlinetta #Ferrari #296GTB #AssettoFiorano #firstlook #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 15, 2021 tagging @astonmartinlagonda, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: The new @astonmartinlagonda Valhalla! Now with a 4.0l twin turbo V8 and two electric motors for a total hybrid output of 950hp. The supercar will go into production in 2023, with a design that has been reworked from the original concept, and it sits in the line beneath Valkyrie but above the future mid-engine sports car that will be the Vanquish. No question, it looks incredible! #AstonMartin #Valhalla #firstlook #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 13, 2021 tagging @photocutout_, @rimac_automobili, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of car and road.

node.text: Full send in the @rimac_automobili Nevera! Turns out it's hilarious and really very, very fast... Awesome shot by @photocutout_ of my ride at @fosgoodwood #Rimac #Nevera #GoodwoodFOS #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 12, 2021 tagging @astonmartinlagonda, @fosgoodwood, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: Who needs a roof! The @astonmartinlagonda V12 Speedster is limited to just 88 cars with a 5.2l TT V12 up front, and the Heritage styling of the DBR1. It might have been raining but that doesn't stop the fun! #AstonMartin #V12Speedster #GoodwoodFOS #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 11, 2021 tagging @mastercarduk, @fosgoodwood, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of standing and outdoors.

node.text: It is my first ever visit to the rally stage for a #Priceless experience with @MastercardUK at @fosgoodwood onboard this 2000 Ford Focus WRC, once driven by @carlossainzoficial. This will be fun! Swipe left to join me on this unique experience. #Mastercard #GoodwoodFOS #FestivalofSpeed #Shmee150 #StartSomethingPriceless #AD

Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 10, 2021 tagging @fosgoodwood, @lotuscars, @jensonbutton, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 2 people, car and road.

node.text: Exciting news, the new @lotuscars Emira is also joining @theshmeemobiles! Better still, I've joined @jensonbutton for an epic run up the @fosgoodwood hillclimb! What a car, the star of the show and a car I'm super excited to have joining the garage next year. More details in the new video! #Lotus #Emira #futureshmeemobile #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 09, 2021 tagging @ferrari, @shmee150wastaken, and @ferrariuk. May be an image of 1 person, car and road.

node.text: Welcome to a future member of @theshmeemobiles, I've ordered a Ferrari SF90 Stradale! What a way to experience it here at @fosgoodwood with a flat out blast in the Spider on the famous hillclimb run. I can't wait for the experience of my first new Ferrari, a 1,000hp hybrid supercar that took my breath away when I drove it a few months ago for the first time. I've got some spec ideas but looking forward to going through the process! Thank you for joining the adventure #Ferrari #SF90 #futureshmeemobile #GoodwoodFOS #FestivalofSpeed #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Tim - Shmee on July 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text: It's good to be back! @fosgoodwood never disappoints and this year the Supercar Paddock is loaded with the latest and greatest including the @astonmartinlagonda Valkyrie. You can spend a lot of time looking at the incredible aero on this car, and that's before you listen to it... More to come! #AstonMartin #Valkyrie #GoodwoodFOS #FestivalofSpeed #SupercarPaddock #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 06, 2021 tagging @lotuscars, and @shmee150wastaken. May be an image of 1 person and car.

node.text: The new @lotuscars Emira! Supercar looks for sports car money and an engine from @mercedesamg to boot. Starting from under £60,000, and available with either the 3.5l Toyota Supercharged V6, or the 2.0l turbo 4-cyl from AMG, this is a serious game changer from Lotus. A mid engine, RWD setup, multiple gearboxes available including manual and DCT, and a lowest weight of 1,405kg, which sounds like a lot of fun to me! #Lotus #Emira #firstlook #Shmee150

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Tim - Shmee on July 05, 2021 tagging @sammooresphoto, @shmee150wastaken, and @f40blu. May be an image of 1 person, car and outdoors.

node.text: Out for a drive in @f40blu with @sammooresphoto as a last run before it's going for sale with @themarket_auctions! I joined the collection day over 6 years ago so we went back to drive the very same roads as a bookend to the ownership, and what a truly special car it is, wearing a bespoke one-off blue, competition pipes and Classiche certification too. The next owner is going to thoroughly enjoy it that's for sure! #Ferrari #F40 #FerrariF40 #Shmee150
